Name: Duality
About the game: Explore the silent story of Duality, a world in which reality has been split into two dimensions. Each level has been beautifully designed with extreme challenge in mind. Will you be able to uncover the secrets that each new challenge holds? Experience Like No Other Unique Gameplay: Dimension-based puzzles Amazing challenges: Created from diverse gameplay elements Immersed Environment: A first-person perspective allows you to feel like you're really a part of this interesting and immersive crafted world Done for the love of it: The first project ever done by Essency Studios, made for the love of the game and the gamers. The answer to every level may not always come easy, but isn't that what makes these so fun?
